      "text": "A 56-year-old man with a history of alcohol-related cirrhosis presents with 2 days of worsening abdominal pain and distension. He denies hematemesis or melena. Vital signs are BP, 100/62 mm Hg; P, 118; R, 22; T, 37.8°C (100.0°F). Physical examination shows abdominal tenderness with shifting dullness and mild scleral icterus. Laboratory studies reveal: WBC 12,500/mm3, platelets 85 × 103/mm3, INR 1.6, AST 78 U/L, ALT 65 U/L, bilirubin 3.5 mg/dL. Bedside ultrasound demonstrates absent flow in the main portal vein with intraluminal echogenic material. What is the most likely diagnosis?",
      "choices": [
        {
          "id": 1,
          "text": "Spontaneous bacterial peritonitis"
        },
        {
          "id": 2,
          "text": "Acute portal vein thrombosis"
        },
        {
          "id": 3,
          "text": "Budd-Chiari syndrome"
        },
        {
          "id": 4,
          "text": "Mesenteric ischemia"
        },
        {
          "id": 5,
          "text": "Variceal hemorrhage"
        }
      ],
      "correct_choice_id": 2,
      "solution": "<div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>A) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=GM0BJg&anker=Z4fb9a359446298e0b5912478808dc7e5\" data-learningcard-id=\"GM0BJg\" data-anker=\"Z4fb9a359446298e0b5912478808dc7e5\" data-sememe-id=\"QE0uv3\">Spontaneous bacterial peritonitis</a> can present with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j50_Pg&anker=Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-learningcard-id=\"j50_Pg\" data-anker=\"Za5de83449ff6a749e6c1348b93b1f3b1\" data-sememe-id=\"CL0q-g\">fever</a>, abdominal <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xN0EWg&anker=Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-learningcard-id=\"xN0EWg\" data-anker=\"Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-section-id=\"NBX-a00\">pain</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=KS0U0f&anker=Z48e76ffce1b364c1ba4dacdd79a56b7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"KS0U0f\" data-anker=\"Z48e76ffce1b364c1ba4dacdd79a56b7b\" data-sememe-id=\"_405NT\">ascites</a> in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=PS0W-2&anker=Za99be06553ff299396a513bb65ed71be\" data-learningcard-id=\"PS0W-2\" data-anker=\"Za99be06553ff299396a513bb65ed71be\" data-sememe-id=\"D401lT\">cirrhosis</a>. However, the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=4n03tg&anker=Z4254d71ea91bb85a18eeeaaf5e7adbef\" data-learningcard-id=\"4n03tg\" data-anker=\"Z4254d71ea91bb85a18eeeaaf5e7adbef\" data-sememe-id=\"fK0kfS\">ultrasound</a> finding of echogenic intraluminal material with absent <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Zf755e99eca186a2dfdaa32b290e1ba0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Zf755e99eca186a2dfdaa32b290e1ba0f\" data-section-id=\"Z8cZOV0\" data-sememe-id=\"VjXGzB\">portal venous</a> flow is not consistent with <span data-sememe-id=\"mucV7V0\">SBP</span>, which is diagnosed via <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=PF0WR3&anker=Z298f094c80caa2931a43acdefb33db7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"PF0WR3\" data-anker=\"Z298f094c80caa2931a43acdefb33db7b\" data-sememe-id=\"qRbCLt\">paracentesis</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #34d399; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>B) CORRECT:</h4>Correct – This patient with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=PS0W-2&anker=Za99be06553ff299396a513bb65ed71be\" data-learningcard-id=\"PS0W-2\" data-anker=\"Za99be06553ff299396a513bb65ed71be\" data-sememe-id=\"D401lT\">cirrhosis</a> presents with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=N50-4g&anker=Z24dc105fa608cb7dad9e5eada9a97d2b\" data-learningcard-id=\"N50-4g\" data-anker=\"Z24dc105fa608cb7dad9e5eada9a97d2b\" data-sememe-id=\"1Qb2Et\">acute abdominal pain</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Z3ae4e1e5581c7405590e65b57fa82021\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Z3ae4e1e5581c7405590e65b57fa82021\" data-section-id=\"KVcUvY0\" data-sememe-id=\"lNbvY8\">tachycardia</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=KS0U0f&anker=Z48e76ffce1b364c1ba4dacdd79a56b7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"KS0U0f\" data-anker=\"Z48e76ffce1b364c1ba4dacdd79a56b7b\" data-sememe-id=\"_405NT\">ascites</a>, and laboratory evidence of hepatic dysfunction. The key diagnostic feature is the absence of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Zf755e99eca186a2dfdaa32b290e1ba0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Zf755e99eca186a2dfdaa32b290e1ba0f\" data-section-id=\"Z8cZOV0\" data-sememe-id=\"VjXGzB\">portal venous</a> flow with intraluminal echogenic material on <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=4n03tg&anker=Z4254d71ea91bb85a18eeeaaf5e7adbef\" data-learningcard-id=\"4n03tg\" data-anker=\"Z4254d71ea91bb85a18eeeaaf5e7adbef\" data-sememe-id=\"fK0kfS\">ultrasound</a>, which is <span data-sememe-id=\"rg0f92\">pathognomonic</span> for <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=DG01Y3&anker=Z8d98d30e81cf30f314ef8a92ef5d6e8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"DG01Y3\" data-anker=\"Z8d98d30e81cf30f314ef8a92ef5d6e8e\" data-sememe-id=\"l9Yvnr\">portal vein thrombosis</a>. <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=DG01Y3&anker=Z8d98d30e81cf30f314ef8a92ef5d6e8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"DG01Y3\" data-anker=\"Z8d98d30e81cf30f314ef8a92ef5d6e8e\" data-sememe-id=\"l9Yvnr\">Portal vein thrombosis</a> occurs in <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=PS0W-2&anker=Za99be06553ff299396a513bb65ed71be\" data-learningcard-id=\"PS0W-2\" data-anker=\"Za99be06553ff299396a513bb65ed71be\" data-sememe-id=\"D401lT\">cirrhosis</a> due to multiple factors including slow portal blood flow from increased intrahepatic resistance, and the complex rebalanced hemostatic state where both <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=8T0Os2&anker=Zd22a919cb2b5c00f82958ca43c767f5b\" data-learningcard-id=\"8T0Os2\" data-anker=\"Zd22a919cb2b5c00f82958ca43c767f5b\" data-section-id=\"X619j30\" data-sememe-id=\"3GcS_d0\">procoagulant</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Tm06Ug&anker=Z868d6a2028d5c175da17ef6f1dc97b5a\" data-learningcard-id=\"Tm06Ug\" data-anker=\"Z868d6a2028d5c175da17ef6f1dc97b5a\" data-section-id=\"fFbkhv\" data-sememe-id=\"vQ0ABf\">anticoagulant</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=8K0ORS&anker=Z6dee07cab92e13d1f6baa3a3ce402f23\" data-learningcard-id=\"8K0ORS\" data-anker=\"Z6dee07cab92e13d1f6baa3a3ce402f23\">proteins</a> are reduced.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>C) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=LL0wyg&anker=Z3f66c3a575919d7020abd9df9ad53bd9\" data-learningcard-id=\"LL0wyg\" data-anker=\"Z3f66c3a575919d7020abd9df9ad53bd9\" data-sememe-id=\"JI0sdh\">Budd-Chiari syndrome</a> results from <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=LJ0wuS&anker=Zee9ce84b414cb2ce8f1c52cf538d7d82\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-anker=\"Zee9ce84b414cb2ce8f1c52cf538d7d82\" data-section-id=\"9I1NUR0\" data-sememe-id=\"Ti16Ig0\">hepatic vein</a> obstruction and typically presents with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=XL09wg&anker=Z709336d8b15286caf8a83fc77a8f0f99\" data-learningcard-id=\"XL09wg\" data-anker=\"Z709336d8b15286caf8a83fc77a8f0f99\" data-section-id=\"eccxYY0\" data-sememe-id=\"RjXlZy\">hepatomegaly</a>, <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=KS0U0f&anker=Z48e76ffce1b364c1ba4dacdd79a56b7b\" data-learningcard-id=\"KS0U0f\" data-anker=\"Z48e76ffce1b364c1ba4dacdd79a56b7b\" data-sememe-id=\"_405NT\">ascites</a>, and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=np07JS&anker=Zf438ec9414d78af41b73470a49bb8221\" data-learningcard-id=\"np07JS\" data-anker=\"Zf438ec9414d78af41b73470a49bb8221\" data-section-id=\"ACcRue0\" data-sememe-id=\"g9bF5D\">right upper quadrant</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xN0EWg&anker=Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-learningcard-id=\"xN0EWg\" data-anker=\"Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-section-id=\"NBX-a00\">pain</a>. While the clinical picture overlaps, the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=4n03tg&anker=Z4254d71ea91bb85a18eeeaaf5e7adbef\" data-learningcard-id=\"4n03tg\" data-anker=\"Z4254d71ea91bb85a18eeeaaf5e7adbef\" data-sememe-id=\"fK0kfS\">ultrasound</a> finding localizes the obstruction to the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=j60_kS&anker=Zf755e99eca186a2dfdaa32b290e1ba0f\" data-learningcard-id=\"j60_kS\" data-anker=\"Zf755e99eca186a2dfdaa32b290e1ba0f\" data-section-id=\"Z8cZOV0\" data-sememe-id=\"VjXGzB\">portal vein</a>, not the <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=LJ0wuS&anker=Zee9ce84b414cb2ce8f1c52cf538d7d82\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-anker=\"Zee9ce84b414cb2ce8f1c52cf538d7d82\" data-section-id=\"9I1NUR0\" data-sememe-id=\"Ti16Ig0\">hepatic veins</a>.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>D) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=LJ0wuS&anker=Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sememe-id=\"xjXEcy\">Mesenteric</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VP0GdT&anker=Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-anker=\"Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-section-id=\"k9cmne0\" data-sememe-id=\"WQ0PEf\">ischemia</a> can cause severe abdominal <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=xN0EWg&anker=Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-learningcard-id=\"xN0EWg\" data-anker=\"Zd673a3f7ee36023aab5a267899e984cc\" data-section-id=\"NBX-a00\">pain</a> with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=rM0fJg&anker=Z3ae4e1e5581c7405590e65b57fa82021\" data-learningcard-id=\"rM0fJg\" data-anker=\"Z3ae4e1e5581c7405590e65b57fa82021\" data-section-id=\"KVcUvY0\" data-sememe-id=\"lNbvY8\">tachycardia</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=wF0h43&anker=Zb1919b7d94d10a63debcb709eaa693f3\" data-learningcard-id=\"wF0h43\" data-anker=\"Zb1919b7d94d10a63debcb709eaa693f3\" data-sememe-id=\"ylYdz6\">leukocytosis</a>, which overlaps with this presentation. However, imaging demonstrates <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=DG01Y3&anker=Z8d98d30e81cf30f314ef8a92ef5d6e8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"DG01Y3\" data-anker=\"Z8d98d30e81cf30f314ef8a92ef5d6e8e\" data-sememe-id=\"l9Yvnr\">portal vein thrombosis</a>, making <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=LJ0wuS&anker=Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-learningcard-id=\"LJ0wuS\" data-anker=\"Z2e7145689ecdf9560060a209d9ae676a\" data-section-id=\"Ja1sl20\" data-sememe-id=\"xjXEcy\">mesenteric</a> <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=VP0GdT&anker=Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-learningcard-id=\"VP0GdT\" data-anker=\"Zbc05e544d46e794a60ac9ce9ec6883af\" data-section-id=\"k9cmne0\" data-sememe-id=\"WQ0PEf\">ischemia</a> less likely in this case.</div><div><h4 style='color: #f87171; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 16px; font-size: 1.125rem;'>E) INCORRECT:</h4>\n<a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Zs0Zth&anker=Z3b12fcfa63d3f70fa0fc718640d0af94\" data-learningcard-id=\"Zs0Zth\" data-anker=\"Z3b12fcfa63d3f70fa0fc718640d0af94\" data-section-id=\"OjWI0l0\" data-sememe-id=\"UE0bE3\">Variceal hemorrhage</a> is a complication of <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=PS0W-2&anker=Za99be06553ff299396a513bb65ed71be\" data-learningcard-id=\"PS0W-2\" data-anker=\"Za99be06553ff299396a513bb65ed71be\" data-sememe-id=\"D401lT\">cirrhosis</a> and <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=LS0wZf&anker=Zd5beacd46243f9dbc75a7032728717a5\" data-learningcard-id=\"LS0wZf\" data-anker=\"Zd5beacd46243f9dbc75a7032728717a5\" data-sememe-id=\"A40RNT\">portal hypertension</a>, often presenting with <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ZS0Zy2&anker=Za867ec17b7a5bf54338ba306e634d927\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZS0Zy2\" data-anker=\"Za867ec17b7a5bf54338ba306e634d927\" data-section-id=\"9E0NB3\" data-sememe-id=\"OT0II2\">hematemesis</a> or <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ZS0Zy2&anker=Z39f22768286d3e3202467c988d3be66a\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZS0Zy2\" data-anker=\"Z39f22768286d3e3202467c988d3be66a\" data-section-id=\"9E0NB3\" data-sememe-id=\"jF0_33\">melena</a>. This patient denies <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=ZS0Zy2&anker=Z5b38a059d860d4f7f79d2947306c643e\" data-learningcard-id=\"ZS0Zy2\" data-anker=\"Z5b38a059d860d4f7f79d2947306c643e\" data-sememe-id=\"M40MPT\">gastrointestinal bleeding</a>, and imaging findings point toward <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=DG01Y3&anker=Z8d98d30e81cf30f314ef8a92ef5d6e8e\" data-learningcard-id=\"DG01Y3\" data-anker=\"Z8d98d30e81cf30f314ef8a92ef5d6e8e\" data-sememe-id=\"l9Yvnr\">portal vein thrombosis</a> rather than active <a href=\"https://www.amboss.com/us/library#xid=Zs0Zth&anker=Z3b12fcfa63d3f70fa0fc718640d0af94\" data-learningcard-id=\"Zs0Zth\" data-anker=\"Z3b12fcfa63d3f70fa0fc718640d0af94\" data-section-id=\"OjWI0l0\" data-sememe-id=\"UE0bE3\">variceal bleeding</a>.</div>",
